T02TD3185E:199a-1: siddhee ae ka b'i ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD3185E:199a-3: dpa' bo gcig tu grub pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3185E:199a-4: sngar bshad pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes la /
T02TD3185E:199a-5: padma dkar po'i steng du yi ge a'a: dkar po las byung ba'i zla ba la yi ge dh'i: dkar po yongs su gyur pa las rje btsun 'jam dpal dpa' bo gcig tu grub pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD3185E:199a-6: sku mdog thams cad dkar ba zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3185E:199a-8: g-yon pas autpala sngon po bsnams pa /
T02TD3185E:199a-9: lha rdzas kyi rgyan dang ldan zhing mdzes pa /
T02TD3185E:199a-10: rnam par bkra pa'i na bza' bsnams nas skyil krung gis bzhugs par bdag nyid skad cig gis rdzogs par byas la /
T02TD3185E:199a-11: mgo bo dang mgrin pa dang /
T02TD3185E:199a-12: snying ga rnams su yi ge aom a'a: h'um rnams dgod par bya'o //
T02TD3185E:199a-13: a'a:'i yi ge dang h'um gi gnyis kyi bar du yang yi ge dh'i:'i 'od zer gyis 'jig rten gyi don byed par gyur pas gsang sngags bzlas par bya ste /
T02TD3185E:199a-14: aom rdo rje rnon pos sdug bsngal gcod //
T02TD3185E:199a-15: shes rab ye shes dag gi sku //
T02TD3185E:199a-16: ye shes sku ste gsung dbang phyug / aa ra pa tsa na dbang 'dud //
T02TD3185E:199a-17: dpa' bo gcig tu grub pa'i sgrub thabs so //
T02TD3185E:199a-18: mkhas pa aa bha ya las tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
